  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.6.3">
<l>pavvanī ruṭaiyāṭai yākac cuṟṟip pārakalan tiruvaṭiyāp pavaṉam meyyā</l>
<l>cevvimā tirameṭṭun tōḷā vaṇṭan tirumuṭiyā niṉṟāṉpāl cella kiṟpīr</l>
<l>kavvaimā kaḷiṟunti veṇṇi yēṟṟak kaḻalmaṉṉar maṇimuṭimēl kāka mēṟa</l>
<l>teyvavāḷ valaṅkoṇṭa cōḻaṉ cērnta tirunaṟaiyūr maṇimāṭañ cērmiṉ kaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who are able to approach near the one who endures,</l>
<l rend="indent">wrapping ocean water as a garment,</l>
<l>With the breadth of the earth as [his] divine feet, the wind as a body,</l>
<l rend="indent">the eight [well-]ordered directions as arms,</l>
<l rend="indent">and the firmament as a crown,</l>
<l>Gather at the beautiful raised shrine in Tirunaṟaiyūr where came the Cōḻa</l>
<l rend="indent">whose sacred sword brought triumph,</l>
<l>So that crows mounted on the jeweled heads of kings with [war] anklets</l>
<l rend="indent">who opposed [him] at Veṇṇi, riding great trumpeting elephants.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
